 by Eclipse Aether repository system implementations and repository connectors. It supplies extension contracts for connector layout, metadata generation, local repository management, and version resolution within the artifact repository system.\\\",\\nmetadata/org.codehaus.woodstox/stax2-api/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Stax2 API extends the standard StAX API for streaming XML processing with additional reader, writer, validation, and utility interfaces. It provides a common higher-level API for features such as typed access and XML validation used by StAX implementations like Woodstox.\\\",\\nmetadata/aopalliance/aopalliance/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"AOP Alliance defines a small set of standard Java interfaces for aspect-oriented programming, especially method and constructor interception. Libraries use these interfaces to expose portable advice and interceptor contracts without depending on a particular AOP implementation.\\\",\\nmetadata/org.apache.santuario/xmlsec/4.0.4/reachability-metadata.json:91:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/org.apache.santuario/xmlsec/4.0.4/reachability-metadata.json:97:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/org.apache.santuario/xmlsec/4.0.4/reachability-metadata.json:103:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/org.apache.santuario/xmlsec/4.0.4/reachability-metadata.json:109:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/javax.jcr/jcr/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Defines the Java Content Repository (JCR) 1.0 API for accessing content repositories independently of a specific implementation. It provides the standard javax.jcr interfaces, classes, and exceptions for sessions, workspaces, nodes, properties, queries, observation, locking, and versioning.\\\",\\nmetadata/org.sonatype.aether/aether-api/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Aether API defines the core interfaces for artifact resolution and repository access in a Maven-style dependency system. It provides contracts for dependency collection, version resolution, and local or remote repository interactions that implementations execute.\\\",\\nmetadata/org.sonatype.aether/aether-spi/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Aether SPI defines service provider interfaces for repository system implementations and repository connectors. It lets implementations plug repository services and connector behavior into the Aether repository system behind its public API.\\\",\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4352:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.ECPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4358:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.ECPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4364:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.ECPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4370:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.ECPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4376:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4382:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4388:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.80.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4394:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.RSAPublicKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4407:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.security.interfaces.ECPrivateKey\\\"\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/reachability-metadata.json:4413:      \\\"type\\\": \\\"java.s